    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. but you said it was a \"qualified success\" because it removed a threat, but now the country is a mess and a breeding ground for extremism. wouldn't a realist argue that any intervention that leaves behind a failed state and more chaos is just a fundamental failure of strategy, regardless of why they did it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
